---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout 
  title="Custom Software Development | Jay Software - 200-400% ROI Solutions"
  description="Eliminate vendor lock-in and forced workarounds. Custom software development that generates 200-400% ROI within 6 months. Free strategic assessment for qualified businesses."
  keywords="custom software development, bespoke software, enterprise software development, business software solutions, ROI software development, scalable software systems"
  canonicalUrl="https://jay-software.com/services/custom-software-development"
>
  
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/20 to-purple-900/20 border-b border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-600/20 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-blue-300 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
            💻 Custom Software Development
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Stop Losing <span class="text-red-400">$15K+/Month</span> to
            <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              Generic Software
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
            Custom software solutions designed specifically for your business processes. Increase efficiency by 60-90% and generate 200-400% ROI within 6 months.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-green-700 hover:to-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Request Custom Software Assessment
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problems Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Is Generic Software <span class="text-red-400">Strangling</span> Your Business?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            Most businesses waste $15K+ monthly fighting against software that wasn't built for them...
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🔒</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Vendor Lock-in Nightmare</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Trapped by expensive software licenses, monthly fees, and limited customization options.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">🔧</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Forced Workarounds</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Your team wastes hours daily adapting business processes to fit rigid software limitations.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-red-500/20 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-red-400 text-2xl mb-4">📈</div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Scaling Roadblocks</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Generic solutions break down as you grow, forcing expensive migrations or multiple tools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
              Custom Software That <span class="text-green-400">Actually Works</span> For Your Business
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
              Built specifically for your workflows, processes, and growth plans. No compromises. No workarounds.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="space-y-8">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-green-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">60-90% Efficiency Increase</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Eliminate manual processes and bottlenecks with software designed for your exact needs.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-blue-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">200-400% ROI Within 6 Months</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Custom solutions pay for themselves through increased productivity and reduced operating costs.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="bg-purple-500/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Scales With Your Growth</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-300">Built to handle 10x growth without performance degradation or expensive upgrades.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What You Get:</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Complete business process analysis & optimization</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Modern, intuitive user interface design</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Secure, scalable backend infrastructure</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Integration with existing systems</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-300">Comprehensive training & ongoing support</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Case Studies -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Custom Software Success Stories
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            Real results from businesses that chose custom over generic
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-green-500/20 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Manufacturing Company</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Replaced 5 different software tools with one custom solution</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">400%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">ROI Increase</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">$45K</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Monthly Savings</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">3 Months</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Payback Period</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic">
              "Our custom software eliminated the need for 5 different tools and saved us 30 hours per week in manual data entry."
            </blockquote>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">E-commerce Business</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Custom inventory management and fulfillment system</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center mb-6">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">250%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">ROI Increase</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">90%</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Error Reduction</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">5x</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-400">Processing Speed</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic">
              "Custom software allowed us to scale from 100 to 1000 orders per day without hiring additional staff."
            </blockquote>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Our Proven <span class="text-green-400">Development Process</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
            From concept to deployment in 8-16 weeks
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-blue-500/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-blue-400 font-bold text-xl">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Discovery & Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Deep dive into your business processes and pain points</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-green-500/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-green-400 font-bold text-xl">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Design & Architecture</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Create detailed specifications and user experience design</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-purple-500/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-purple-400 font-bold text-xl">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Development & Testing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Agile development with regular feedback and testing</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="bg-amber-500/20 w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-amber-400 font-bold text-xl">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Deployment & Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Launch, training, and ongoing optimization</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-purple-900/20 border-t border-slate-700">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
            Ready to Build Software That <span class="text-green-400">Actually Works</span> For You?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
            Stop fighting against generic software. Get a custom solution that grows your business.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/#strategic-consultation" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-blue-600 hover:from-green-700 hover:to-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
              Request Custom Software Assessment
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/" 
               class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition-all duration-300">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
              </svg>
              Back to Home
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout> 